        <h1>Forum Guidelines</h1>
        <p>Welcome to our forum! To ensure a positive and productive environment for all members, please follow these guidelines:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Be Respectful:</strong> Treat all members with respect. Personal attacks, harassment, and hate speech are not tolerated.</li>
          <li><strong>Stay On Topic:</strong> Please keep discussions relevant to the topic at hand. Off-topic posts may be removed.</li>
          <li><strong>No Spam:</strong> Avoid posting unsolicited advertisements, links, or repetitive content.</li>
          <li><strong>Privacy:</strong> Do not share personal information about yourself or others. Protect your privacy and respect the privacy of others.</li>
          <li><strong>Report Issues:</strong> If you encounter inappropriate behavior or content, report it to the moderators.</li>
          <li><strong>Follow the Rules:</strong> Adhere to the specific rules of each sub-forum. They may have additional guidelines.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>By participating in this forum, you agree to abide by these guidelines. Let's work together to maintain a friendly and welcoming community!</p>
